quickjs.library/QJS_AddRegExp                       quickjs.library/QJS_AddRegExp

    NAME
	QJS_AddRegExp -- Install RegExp runtime support.

    SYNOPSIS
	QJS_AddRegExp(ctx)
		      A0

	VOID QJS_AddRegExp(JSContext *ctx);

