quickjs.library/QJS_AddRegExpCompiler         QJS_AddRegExpCompiler

    NAME
	QJS_AddRegExpCompiler -- Install the RegExp parser/
	    compiler.

    SYNOPSIS
	QJS_AddRegExpCompiler(ctx)
			      A0

	VOID QJS_AddRegExpCompiler(JSContext *ctx);

