quickjs.library/QJS_AddBigInt                       quickjs.library/QJS_AddBigInt

    NAME
	QJS_AddBigInt -- Install BigInt support.

    SYNOPSIS
	QJS_AddBigInt(ctx)
		      A0

	VOID QJS_AddBigInt(JSContext *ctx);

